OL,3,CRescuers race to reach people trapped
OL,4,Cfor nearly a week in Laos cave
OL,6,FRescuers are racing to save seven
OL,7,Fpeople who have been trapped in a cave
OL,8,Fin Laos for nearly a week.
OL,10,FThe villagers went into the cave in
OL,11,Fthe central Laotian province of
OL,12,FXaisomboun last Wednesday to search
OL,13,Ffor gold, but heavy rain triggered
OL,14,Fflash flooding which blocked the exit,
OL,15,Flocal rescue teams said.
OL,17,FTwo Thai divers and a Finnish expert
OL,18,Fwho helped with the 2018 cave rescue
OL,19,Fof a youth football team in Thailand
OL,20,Fhave joined the operation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
