CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779843788
OL,3,CRescuers race to reach people trapped
OL,4,Cfor nearly a week in Laos cave
OL,6,FThe locals are believed to be trapped
OL,7,Fdeep inside the cave on "an elevated
OL,8,Fledge" with continuous airflow,
OL,9,Faccording to the state-run Lao News
OL,10,FAgency.
OL,12,FTo reach them, rescuers will have to
OL,13,Fnavigate a 340 metre tunnel, according
OL,14,Fto the Metta Tham Kalasin (MTK)
OL,15,FCommand and Control Centre, one of the
OL,16,Fgroups coordinating the rescue.
OL,18,FHelmets, breathing masks and gas
OL,19,Fmonitors are being used as rescuers
OL,20,Fwill also have to crawl through tight
OL,21,F60cm tunnels to reach the group.
OL,26,@oD@YOU
