PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779843788
OL,3,CRescuers race to reach people trapped
OL,4,Cfor nearly a week in Laos cave
OL,6,FThe rescue operation is taking place
OL,7,Fin a mountainous area near Long Tieng
OL,8,Fin Xaisomboun province, known for its
OL,9,Fsweeping valleys and rich mineral
OL,10,Freserves.
OL,12,FAuthorities were alerted to the
OL,13,Ftrapped residents by a member of the
OL,14,Fgroup who managed to escape before the
OL,15,Fexit was blocked, Bounkham Luanglath,
OL,16,Fwho leads Laos' Rescue Volunteer for
OL,17,FPeople, said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
