OL,3,CRescuers race to reach people trapped
OL,4,Cfor nearly a week in Laos cave
OL,6,FLocals frequently visit the site to
OL,7,Fsearch for gold deposits despite
OL,8,Frepeated safety warnings from the
OL,9,Fauthorities, Luanglath added.
